snippet.title: One Wheel Studio
snippet.description:
I'm just one guy making games with Unity in his spare time. I use Blender and Unity to create my games and my tutorials. This is my channel showing the results of my efforts.

I teach a high school game design course that is focused on the basics of using Unity, Blender and Magicavoxel. I've used Playmaker, Bolt and most recently the class has moved to C#.

Got questions? Like what you see? Come join the discussion on Discord: discord.onewheelstudio.com

I also produce custom tutorial videos and currently produce the Odin Inspector tutorials. Need a tutorial, promo or review video? Find more information at: https://onewheelstudio.com/customvideos
